370
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:56,040
<i>Can he bag himself a podium</i>

371
00:23:56,120 --> 00:23:59,600
<i>and stay ahead of Alex Albon
in the Red Bull just behind him?</i>

372
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:05,440
<i>Pérez, once again,
has put in a super performance.</i>

373
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:08,320
<i>Last two laps,
two tenths quicker than Albon.</i>

374
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:12,480
<i>Your lap time
is getting closer to Verstappen's.</i>

375
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:17,640
<i>Only three laps left
