640
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:24,520
<i>It's a slow stop for Bottas.</i>

641
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:30,000
<i>There's a man waving on the front left.
They can't get the wheel on at all!</i>

642
00:42:30,080 --> 00:42:32,240
<i>Disastrous pit stop for Mercedes.</i>

643
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,880
<i>There's been a big problem
