651
00:43:01,080 --> 00:43:03,200
<i>Russell is going to have to pit again.</i>

652
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:06,280
<i>Absolute disaster for the Mercedes team.</i>

653
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:11,680
Come on! Come on!

654
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:16,760
<i>We are now the lead car.
Russell has also boxed.</i>

655
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:20,160
<i>Mercedes have dropped an absolute clanger.</i>

656
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:22,320
<i>Pérez now leading the Grand Prix.</i>

657
00:43:26,600 --> 00:43:27,960
I can hardly speak.

658
00:43:28,560 --> 00:43:31,160
<i>Yes, Checo, this is really good.
Maximum push.</i>

659
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:35,360
<i>Sergio Pérez on the verge
of winning his first ever Grand Prix,</i>

660
00:43:35,440 --> 00:43:38,160
<i>having been in last place
