664
00:43:50,200 --> 00:43:52,240
<i>has just half a lap to go.</i>

665
00:43:56,680 --> 00:43:59,520
<i>The man who was
in last place at the end of lap one</i>

666
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:03,080
