667
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:06,800
<i>Yes, Checo!</i>

668
00:44:06,880 --> 00:44:08,880
<i>Sergio Pérez, wow!</i>

669
00:44:14,880 --> 00:44:16,520
<i>Yes, Checo, P1!</i>

670
00:44:17,520 --> 00:44:18,520
<i>Yes!</i>

671
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:27,120
I'm speechless, guys.

672
00:44:28,560 --> 00:44:30,200
<i>Amazing, Checo, well done.</i>

673
00:44:49,040 --> 00:44:51,880
Checo! Checo! Checo!

674
00:44:51,960 --> 00:44:55,040
- Checo! Checo! Checo!
- Yeah, Checo!

675
00:44:56,480 --> 00:44:58,640
<i>Look at those celebrations.</i>

676
00:45:00,480 --> 00:45:04,080
<i>And it's the first ever double podium
